trans-unit.source: Provides properties and methods for evaluating and editing a resource expression at design time.
trans-unit.target: Inneholder egenskaper og metoder for evaluering og redigering av et uttrykk som ressursen under utformingen.

trans-unit.source: The ResourceExpressionEditor class derives from the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ExpressionEditor> class and provides an implementation for evaluating and associating a resource reference with a control property at design time.
trans-unit.target: Klassen ResourceExpressionEditor er avledet fra den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ExpressionEditor>klasse og inneholder en implementering for evaluering og knytte en ressursreferanse til en kontrollegenskapen under utformingen.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ExpressionEditor>

trans-unit.source: For example, you can bind the value of a control property to the resource expression `Resources:submitText`, which indicates that the control property value is set using the resource named `submitText`.
trans-unit.target: Du kan for eksempel binde verdien for en kontrollegenskapen til ressurs-uttrykket `Resources:submitText`, noe som angir at egenskapsverdien kontrollen angis ved hjelp av ressursen `submitText`.

trans-unit.source: A visual designer host, such as [!INCLUDE[vsprvslong](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)], uses the ResourceExpressionEditor class to specify a resource class, key, and designer default value for a resource expression, and then evaluate the selected resource expression for design-time rendering.
trans-unit.target: Visuelle utformeren vert, for eksempel [!INCLUDE[vsprvslong](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)], bruker ResourceExpressionEditor klasse til å angi en ressurs-klasse, og designer standard verdi for et uttrykk for ressursen og evaluere det valgte uttrykket for utforming gjengivelse.

trans-unit.source: When you browse the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.HtmlControlDesigner.Expressions%2A> property for a control in the design-time properties grid, the visual designer displays a dialog box to set expressions that provide the run-time value for a control property.
trans-unit.target: Når du blar gjennom den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.HtmlControlDesigner.Expressions%2A>-egenskapen for en kontroll i rutenettet utformingen egenskaper den visuelle utformeren vises en dialogboks til et angitt uttrykk som yter kjøretid for en kontrollegenskap.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.HtmlControlDesigner.Expressions%2A>

trans-unit.source: You can select the expression type based on a list of expression prefixes.
trans-unit.target: Du kan velge uttrykkstypen basert på en liste over uttrykk prefikser.

trans-unit.source: When you select the **Resources** expression prefix in the list, the visual designer uses the ResourceExpressionEditor methods to set, evaluate, and convert the expression based on the resource expression syntax.
trans-unit.target: Når du merker av **ressurser** som uttrykksprefiks i listen, den visuelle utformeren bruker ResourceExpressionEditor-metoder for å angi, evaluere og konvertere uttrykk som er basert på syntaksen til ressurs-uttrykk.

trans-unit.source: The visual designer uses the evaluated expression result to assign control property values that are rendered on the design surface.
trans-unit.target: Den visuelle utformeren bruker resultatet evaluerte uttrykket til å tilordne kontrollen egenskapsverdiene som gjengis på utformingsoverflaten.

trans-unit.source: The base <xref:System.Web.Configuration.ExpressionBuilder.ExpressionPrefix%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property for a <xref:System.Web.Compilation.ResourceExpressionBuilder> returns the string `Resources`.
trans-unit.target: Grunntallet <xref:System.Web.Configuration.ExpressionBuilder.ExpressionPrefix%2A?displayProperty=fullName>-egenskapen for et <xref:System.Web.Compilation.ResourceExpressionBuilder>returnerer strengen `Resources`.</xref:System.Web.Compilation.ResourceExpressionBuilder> </xref:System.Web.Configuration.ExpressionBuilder.ExpressionPrefix%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.Compilation.ResourceExpressionBuilder> class is associated with the expression prefix `Resources` and the ResourceExpressionEditor implementation.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.Compilation.ResourceExpressionBuilder>klassen som er knyttet til uttrykket prefikset `Resources` og ResourceExpressionEditor implementeringen.</xref:System.Web.Compilation.ResourceExpressionBuilder>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ResourceExpressionEditor.EvaluateExpression%2A> method evaluates an input resource expression.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ResourceExpressionEditor.EvaluateExpression%2A>metoden evaluerer et uttrykk som inndata ressursen.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ResourceExpressionEditor.EvaluateExpression%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ExpressionEditor.GetExpressionEditorSheet%2A> method returns the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ExpressionEditorSheet> implementation that is used to select the resource name, class, and designer default value, and to form a resource expression from the selected resource values.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ExpressionEditor.GetExpressionEditorSheet%2A>metoden returnerer den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ExpressionEditorSheet>Implementeringstypen som brukes til å velge ressursnavn, klassen og designer standardverdien og å utgjøre et uttrykk som ressursen fra verdiene for ressursen som er valgt.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ExpressionEditorSheet> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ExpressionEditor.GetExpressionEditorSheet%2A>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of a <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.ResourceExpressionEditor"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av en <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.ResourceExpressionEditor"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ResourceExpressionEditor> object is configured by the base class together with an <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ExpressionEditor.ExpressionPrefix%2A> property set to `Resources`.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ResourceExpressionEditor>objektet er konfigurert av basisklassen sammen med en <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ExpressionEditor.ExpressionPrefix%2A>-egenskapen satt til `Resources`.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ExpressionEditor.ExpressionPrefix%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ResourceExpressionEditor>

trans-unit.source: Evaluates a resource expression and provides the design-time value for a control property.
trans-unit.target: Evaluerer et uttrykk, og inneholder verdien for utforming for en kontrollegenskap.

trans-unit.source: The EvaluateExpression method looks up the resource that is specified by `expression`, and then returns the resource.
trans-unit.target: Metoden EvaluateExpression slår opp ressursen som er angitt i `expression`, og returnerer ressursen.

trans-unit.source: The visual designer uses the EvaluateExpression method to evaluate a resource expression and provide the design-time value for an associated control property.
trans-unit.target: Den visuelle utformeren bruker EvaluateExpression-metoden til å evaluere et uttrykk for ressursen og angi verdien for utforming for en egenskap for tilknyttede kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: At run time, the page parser uses the <xref:System.Web.Compilation.ResourceExpressionBuilder.EvaluateExpression%2A> and <xref:System.Web.Compilation.ResourceExpressionBuilder.GetCodeExpression%2A> methods of the corresponding <xref:System.Web.Compilation.ResourceExpressionBuilder> implementation to evaluate an expression and provide the run-time value for an associated control property.
trans-unit.target: Siden parseren bruker under kjøring av <xref:System.Web.Compilation.ResourceExpressionBuilder.EvaluateExpression%2A>og <xref:System.Web.Compilation.ResourceExpressionBuilder.GetCodeExpression%2A>metoder for den tilsvarende <xref:System.Web.Compilation.ResourceExpressionBuilder>implementering evaluere et uttrykk for å angi verdien kjøretid for en egenskap for tilknyttede kontrollen.</xref:System.Web.Compilation.ResourceExpressionBuilder> </xref:System.Web.Compilation.ResourceExpressionBuilder.GetCodeExpression%2A> </xref:System.Web.Compilation.ResourceExpressionBuilder.EvaluateExpression%2A>

trans-unit.source: The visual designer uses the <xref:System.Web.Compilation.ResourceExpressionBuilder.ParseExpression%2A> method to parse the expression string at design time, and then calls the EvaluateExpression method with the parsed expression data.
trans-unit.target: Den visuelle utformeren bruker den <xref:System.Web.Compilation.ResourceExpressionBuilder.ParseExpression%2A>metode for å analysere uttrykk-strengen ved utformingen, og kaller deretter metoden EvaluateExpression med datatypen analysere uttrykk.</xref:System.Web.Compilation.ResourceExpressionBuilder.ParseExpression%2A>

trans-unit.source: A resource expression to evaluate.
trans-unit.target: En ressurs uttrykk som skal evalueres.

trans-unit.source: `expression` does not include the <xref uid="langword_csharp_Resources" name="Resources" href=""></xref> expression prefix.
trans-unit.target: `expression`inneholder ikke den <xref uid="langword_csharp_Resources" name="Resources" href=""> </xref> uttrykksprefiks.

trans-unit.source: An object supplying additional parse data, in the form of a <xref href="System.Web.Compilation.ResourceExpressionFields"></xref> value.
trans-unit.target: Et objekt ekstra spaltes data, i form av en <xref href="System.Web.Compilation.ResourceExpressionFields"> </xref> verdi.

trans-unit.source: The type of the control property.
trans-unit.target: Typen for kontrollegenskapen.

trans-unit.source: A service provider implementation supplied by the designer host, used to obtain additional design-time services.
trans-unit.target: En tjenesten leverandøren implementering angitt av designer verten, brukes til å hente utformingen tilleggstjenester.

trans-unit.source: The object referenced by the evaluated expression string, if the expression evaluation succeeded; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Objektet refererer til den evaluerte Uttrykksstrengen hvis uttrykket evalueringen lyktes; Ellers <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Returns a resource expression editor sheet that is initialized with the input expression string and service provider implementation.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer en ressurs uttrykket redigeringsprogrammet for som er initialisert med inndatauttrykk streng og tjenesten leverandøren implementeringen.

trans-unit.source: The GetExpressionEditorSheet method returns an expression editor sheet implementation for resource expressions.
trans-unit.target: Metoden GetExpressionEditorSheet returnerer et uttrykk redigeringsprogram arket implementering for ressursen uttrykk.

trans-unit.source: The visual designer host uses the expression editor sheet in its expressions dialog box.
trans-unit.target: Visuelle designer verten bruker uttrykket redigeringsprogrammet arket i uttrykksdialogboksen.

trans-unit.source: A resource expression, used to initialize the expression editor sheet.
trans-unit.target: Et uttrykk, brukes til å starte uttrykket redigeringsprogrammet arket.

trans-unit.source: A service provider implementation supplied by the designer host, used to initialize the expression editor sheet.
trans-unit.target: En tjenesten leverandøren implementering angitt av designer verten, brukes til å starte uttrykket redigeringsprogrammet arket.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.ResourceExpressionEditorSheet"></xref> that defines the resource expression properties.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.ResourceExpressionEditorSheet"> </xref> som definerer uttrykket ressursegenskaper.
